Tools Needed To Build A Small Robot



    Raspberry Pi Model 3 Or 4
    Motor controller board
    2 × 3V - 6V DC motors
    2 OR 4 wheels
    1 × AA battery holder
    4 × AA batteries
    Ball caster
    Wire or jumper leads
    USB Battery pack
    Soldering iron and solder
    Wire strippers
    Small Form Of Box Or Case Suitable For This Build 
